║  24.3K tokens saved      $0.06 avoided  ║
║  12 sessions              47 commands   ║
║                                         ║
║  Top Commands:                          ║
║    ctx_read ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓ 18             ║
║    git      ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓ 12                 ║
║    ctx_shell ▓▓▓▓▓ 8                   ║
║                                         ║
║  Cache Hit Rate: 65%                    ║
